snippet.title: Factoring Using the Great Common Factor, GCF - Example 2 - Factoring Out Binomials
snippet.description:
Thanks to all of you who support me on Patreon. You da real mvps!   $1 per month helps!! :)  https://www.patreon.com/patrickjmt !! Factoring Using the Great Common Factor, GCF - Example 2.
In this video, I do two examples of factoring out the greatest common factor to rewrite a polynomial expression.  In this video, we must factor out binomial expressions.
